sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Laptop as 💻 Laptop Browser
    participant Gateway as 🛡️ nginx_gateway
    participant App as 📦 app_backend_1
    participant DB as 🔒 postgres_db

    Note over Laptop,Gateway: Public Plain/Encrypted Data Pipeline
    Laptop->>Gateway: HTTP Request (Port 8080)
    Gateway->>App: Forward Request (Segment A)

    Note over App,DB: Zero-Trust mTLS Pipeline (Segment B)
    App->>DB: 1. TLS Handshake: ClientHello
    DB->>App: 2. ServerHello + Sends postgres.crt
    Note over App: App verifies DB identity<br>using rootCA.crt
    App->>DB: 3. Sends app_backend.crt + Client Key Exchange
    Note over DB: DB verifies App identity<br>using rootCA.crt
    App->>DB: 4. Establishes Cryptographic Tunnel

    App->>DB: 🔒 Encrypted SQL Query (TLS 1.3)
    DB->>App: 🔒 Encrypted Data Result
    App->>Gateway: HTTP Response
    Gateway->>Laptop: HTTP Response Result